{"tid":2051302,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"學生動源 宣佈：原定 6/7 九龍遊行將會 延期舉行","createTime":"2020-06-04T16:07:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-04T18:07:11.000Z","uid":219007,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8efbfa48d112f4bb57478f0362748a53a4749e94","tid":2051302,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T16:07:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/pns/港聞/article/20200604/s00002/1591209980533/警反對學生動源周日遊行-指「理念支持勇武抗爭」\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20200604%2Fs00002%2F1591209980533%2F%E8%AD%A6%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E5%8B%95%E6%BA%90%E5%91%A8%E6%97%A5%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C-%E6%8C%87%E3%80%8C%E7%90%86%E5%BF%B5%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E5%8B%87%E6%AD%A6%E6%8A%97%E7%88%AD%E3%80%8D&d=OUx24mKaoEPTVTG9WcU5EjcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=6ceda36e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20200604%2Fs00002%2F1591209980533%2F%E8%AD%A6%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E5%8B%95%E6%BA%90%E5%91%A8%E6%97%A5%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C-%E6%8C%87%E3%80%8C%E7%90%86%E5%BF%B5%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E5%8B%87%E6%AD%A6%E6%8A%97%E7%88%AD%E3%80%8D&h=3c65969c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/pns/港聞/article/20200604/s00002/1591209980533/警反對學生動源周日遊行-指「理念支持勇武抗爭」</a><br />\n<br />\n2020/6/4<br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】反修例運動即將一周年，食衛局前日宣布將原本今日屆滿的8人限聚令延長14日，「學生動源」原定周日（7日）於九龍區舉辦遊行，警方昨日發出反對通知書，考慮因素除了有禁聚令，還有學生動源「理念是支持勇武抗爭」，「過往紀錄顯示有相關主題的遊行，最終都會作出嚴重暴力違法行為」。學生動源表示強烈不滿，惟不會上訴，遊行會延期舉行。<br />\n<br />\n學生動源發聲明，對警方發出反對通知書理由表示強烈不滿；質疑警方是否日後一切有關遊行均不會發不反對通知書，又引述基本法指香港居民有集會、遊行、示威的自由，「警方無權禁止任何有關活動」。聲明又稱由於限聚令延長，遊行獲發不反對通知書機會甚低，將不會為7日的遊行上訴，遊行會延期。"},{"pid":"3f15fd8c6676df15bac2661139bdc5d9bce07cf5","tid":2051302,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T16:10:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dbbe7b15480ea65667e3a842d8af58777a46920","tid":2051302,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T17:12:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61ea8dc2608cf4a64856424cfb771968bb48981a","tid":2051302,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T18:07:11.000Z","msg":"佢地只係學生<br />\n唔好屌"}]}